# Eazadmin Web App Cursor Rules

## Mobile/Web Component Separation (Required)

- This web app must not import or reuse UI components from mobile apps.
- Never import from `saiisai` or `saiisaiseller` component paths.
- If a feature exists on mobile and web, implement separate components for web.
- Do not create cross-platform shared frontend component folders/packages.

# Shared project skills

See .cursor/skills/ for confirmed tokens, security rules,
API response shapes, image pipeline, and cross-app consistency rules.
These skills take precedence over any assumptions.
